title: Cottage Country
text:
I took this at a cottage my family rented north of Gooderham, Ont., the summer of 2013. It was the most amazing sunset that I had ever seen, so I was thrilled to capture the image. Afterward I hung a framed poster size photo on my kitchen wall. It always reminds me of the incredible beauty in our own backyard. â€“Laurie Jewell
